524
00:34:20,740 --> 00:34:23,730
No money.No husband.

525
00:34:23,730 --> 00:34:25,900
No family.Two kids to raise.

526
00:34:25,900 --> 00:34:27,550
Your mom deserved better from you.

527
00:34:27,550 --> 00:34:30,300
She filled our heads with empty promises and lies!

528
00:34:30,300 --> 00:34:33,210
She was trying to protect you.

529
00:34:34,920 --> 00:34:37,190
She didn't protect us.

530
00:34:37,190 --> 00:34:39,320
She left us when we needed her the most.

531
00:34:39,320 --> 00:34:42,150
But she came looking for you,didn't she,natalie?

532
00:34:42,330 --> 00:34:44,590
After you ran off.

533
00:34:46,620 --> 00:34:48,260
Yeah,she found me.

534
00:34:48,260 --> 00:34:50,130
Where?

535
00:34:50,160 --> 00:34:52,470
Home.

536
00:35:10,900 --> 00:35:13,640
I thought I might find you here.

537
00:35:17,750 --> 00:35:20,770
You have every right to be angry.

538
00:35:27,260 --> 00:35:30,060
But I'm doing my best,natalie.

539
00:35:30,060 --> 00:35:32,980
Why can't you be real for once,mom?

540
00:35:33,690 --> 00:35:36,150
You want to know what's real,nat?

541
00:35:36,390 --> 00:35:39,090
I never thought I'd be a widow.

542
00:35:40,220 --> 00:35:43,220
I never thought I'd lose our home.

543
00:35:43,480 --> 00:35:45,340
Your dad always took care of everything.

544
00:35:45,340 --> 00:35:48,060
All I had to do was love you and your sister.

545
00:35:48,060 --> 00:35:51,870
Maybe it's not enough,mom-- love.

546
00:35:53,680 --> 00:35:56,460
It's all I've got.

547
00:36:06,060 --> 00:36:09,340
How could he die on me?

548
00:36:13,370 --> 00:36:15,860
Still got each other,mom.

549
00:36:18,650 --> 00:36:21,410
The bradford girls,remember?

550
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:25,460
we stick together.

551
00:36:27,060 --> 00:36:30,300
We got to go forward with what we've got.

552
00:36:32,680 --> 00:36:35,320
Still got this,too.

553
00:36:36,290 --> 00:36:39,630
- A lottery ticket?
- It's a hope ticket.

554
00:36:43,100 --> 00:36:45,700
It's worth a try,right?

555
00:36:52,350 --> 00:36:54,420
It's a winner.

556
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:56,070
25 bucks.

557
00:36:56,070 --> 00:36:58,830
