558
00:36:58,830 --> 00:37:01,870
And I can still pay the finder's fee.

559
00:37:02,870 --> 00:37:05,060
How about I drive you to school?

560
00:37:05,060 --> 00:37:07,600
And when you and abby get home,

561
00:37:08,560 --> 00:37:11,570
we'll have a real birthday celebration.

562
00:37:13,780 --> 00:37:17,490
