605
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:38,780
- what do you mean?
- The million we won.

606
00:39:38,890 --> 00:39:40,490
Million?

607
00:39:41,080 --> 00:39:42,750
hopper,you know how this works.

608
00:39:42,750 --> 00:39:44,550
You're lucky if you win two bucks.

609
00:39:44,550 --> 00:39:47,080
No,I'm going to get my wife back.

610
00:39:47,080 --> 00:39:49,560
I'm going to play baseball with my son.

611
00:39:49,670 --> 00:39:52,680
He wants that special glove,and I'm going to get it for him.

612
00:39:52,680 --> 00:39:54,390
Hopper...

613
00:39:54,390 --> 00:39:57,310
that picture was from a long time ago.

614
00:39:57,380 --> 00:39:58,680
You know that.

615
00:39:58,680 --> 00:39:59,970
No,no.

616
00:40:00,910 --> 00:40:03,500
