618
00:40:08,010 --> 00:40:10,440
He's a grown man.

619
00:40:12,670 --> 00:40:14,970
He is?

620
00:40:15,710 --> 00:40:17,880
What's past is past.

621
00:40:18,490 --> 00:40:20,960
